    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>踏入一片虚幻之地</strong>：手握一台录像机，徜徉于无视物理法则延展的黄色走廊。在这片诡异的迷宫中，沉默本身化作无处不在的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302570/extras/872f05d1c5ce6a0e5d185a8666f24c11.avif?t=1771078531\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302570/extras_big/872f05d1c5ce6a0e5d185a8666f24c11.avif?t=1771078531 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >后室<strong>剥离了传统恐怖游戏的元素</strong>，创造出一种更原始的体验——一<strong>种纯粹的心理感受</strong>，在这里，<strong>你的想象将成为最可怕的敌人</strong>。獨自一人、嗡嗡作响的荧光灯，以及那种愈发强烈的疲想：这些走廊正在注视着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302570/extras/7e018efe89ac428142df677545ac40ef.avif?t=1771078531\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302570/extras_big/7e018efe89ac428142df677545ac40ef.avif?t=1771078531 width=800 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 纯粹的氛围</strong>：没有怪物、谜题或目标，完全专注于体验本身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 真实的錄影機美学</strong>：以复古视角记录你的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 多样化的独特区域</strong>：每一片区域都更加抽象与令人不安。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 极简声音设计</strong>：荧光灯的嗡鸣声、回响的脚步声、令人窒息的静谧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 零界面元素</strong>：没有任何干扰，完全沉浸其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302570/extras/a4a459de64961fe65bfb868330c11a39.avif?t=1771078531\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302570/extras_big/a4a459de64961fe65bfb868330c11a39.avif?t=1771078531 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否足够勇敢，去直面后室那无垠的虚空？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款受后室概念启发的独立游戏，虽汲取了后室现象的灵感，但与Kane Pixels的作品及后室Wiki和Fandom无任何关联。</p>",
